# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:13
translate chinese lisas4_e3316aae:

    # sp "I'd need a few days to list them all."
    sp "要列出所有人的话，我得花好几天。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:14
translate chinese lisas4_5402352e:

    # sp "There's my ex-husband, Suzy's dad, who was a complete waste of time."
    sp "有我的前夫，苏茜的爸爸，那人简直是浪费时间。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:16
translate chinese lisas4_dd7ccef3:

    # sp "But he gave me Suzy, so I can't complain too much."
    sp "但他给了我苏茜，所以我也不好抱怨太多。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:18
translate chinese lisas4_9aed485d:

    # sp "Then there's your dad, who I love, but I think I ruined that relationship."
    sp "还有你的爸爸，我很爱他，但我觉得是我搞砸了那段关系。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:19
translate chinese lisas4_a2a6fb65:

    # pc "What do you mean?"
    pc "你什么意思？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:21
translate chinese lisas4_ae8030f5:

    # sp "I didn't give him the attention that he really needed."
    sp "我没有给他真正需要的关注。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:22
translate chinese lisas4_b1130f91:

    # sp "For a while, it was good. Really good."
    sp "有一阵子，关系很好。真的很好。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:23
translate chinese lisas4_465845f5:

    # sp "But eventually that all faded away."
    sp "但最终这一切都消逝了。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:24
translate chinese lisas4_a977be26:

    # sp "When your dad started working in the basement all the time, instead of fighting for him, I became hurt and started resenting him."
    sp "当你爸爸开始整天泡在地下室工作时，我本该为他争取，但我却感到受伤，开始怨恨他。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:25
translate chinese lisas4_a394726b:

    # sp "And that just made things worse. My feelings of resentment compounding every day."
    sp "这反而让事情变得更糟。我的怨恨感每天都在加剧。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:27
translate chinese lisas4_d002892e:

    # sp "I still loved him. I still DO love him. But I also became so mad at him."
    sp "我依然爱他。我现在依然爱他。但我同时也对他非常生气。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:28
translate chinese lisas4_10ac4dc5:

    # sp "I felt like he abandoned me, leaving me for his work."
    sp "我觉得他抛弃了我，为了工作而离开了我。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:30
translate chinese lisas4_4da79f9e:

    # sp "Then he really did leave."
    sp "后来他真的离开了。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:31
translate chinese lisas4_8606aa79:

    # sp "I should have fought harder. That's my biggest regret."
    sp "我本该更努力争取的。这是我最大的遗憾。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:32
translate chinese lisas4_f5b70f93:

    # pc "Sorry [mom]. You know it's not your fault though, right?"
    pc "对不起，[mom]。不过你知道这不是你的错，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:34
translate chinese lisas4_36c76732:

    # sp "Most of me knows that. But then some part of me still feels like I should have been able to do something."
    sp "我大部分时候都明白这一点。但内心深处总觉得，我本该做点什么的。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:35
translate chinese lisas4_32d29ad9:

    # pc "I love you, [mom]."
    pc "我爱你，[mom]。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/LisaConversations/lisas4.rpy:36
translate chinese lisas4_4e2b3e30:

    # sp "I love you too, honey."
    sp "我也爱你，亲爱的。"

